FileCompressor - Spring Boot
This is a simple file compressor built using Spring Boot. It provides RESTful APIs to perform compression on a .txt file into binary code and decompression of .txt file of binary code to it's orginal content.


Features

Compression - Compresses a normal text file 
Decompression - Decopresses a compressed file into it's orginal form


Technologies Used

Spring Boot - Backend framework
Spring MVC - RESTful API handling


API Endpoints

GET  /api/compress/compressText -> Compress a text file
POST /api/compress/decompressText -> Decompress a compressed file into it's original form 
